                <note rend="inline" type="source">File No. 312.115/15.</note>
                <head>
                    <hi rend="italic">The <gloss type="from">Acting Secretary of State</gloss> to
                        Consul <persName type="to">Alger</persName>.</hi>
                </head>
                <opener>
                    <seg rendition="#center">[Telegram.]</seg>
                </opener>
                <opener>
                    <dateline rendition="#right">
                        <placeName>
                            <hi rend="smallcaps">Department of State</hi>, <lb/>
                            <hi rend="italic">Washington</hi>
                        </placeName>, <date calendar="gregorian" when="1913-10-08">
                            <hi rend="italic">October 8, 1913</hi>
                        </date>.</dateline>
                </opener>
                <p>Your October 6th. Informally protest to Riveros against forced loan from Rosario
                    Mining Company.</p>
                <closer>
                    <signed>
                        <hi rend="smallcaps">Moore</hi>
                    </signed>.</closer>
            </div>
        </body>
